Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.75,0:00:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva Heinemann?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.66,0:00:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.49,0:00:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though she's fallen so far, her\Npersonality hasn't changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.93,0:00:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, she might have gotten worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.03,0:00:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she mention where she was staying?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.60,0:00:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she said she didn't have much cash on her...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.91,0:00:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,so she was going back to her hotel to get some.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.57,0:00:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how long she'll continue to think\Nshe's a wealthy man's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Which hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.81,0:00:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She said it was the Hotel Staiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.82,0:00:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she'll really pay her tab...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.92,0:00:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,staying at a third-rate hotel like that and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.86,0:00:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.29,0:00:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you that man she was engaged to?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.96,0:00:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He was...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.44,0:00:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, is this the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.14,0:00:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I just saw that serial killer who was...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.41,0:00:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:00:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen my coat?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I hung it up on the coat hanger by the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:38.47,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,0)\pos(360,340)}Room 402
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.61,0:03:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.81,0:03:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be an Eva...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,a woman named Eva Heinemann staying at your hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.98,0:03:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, I'll connect you to her room.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please wait a moment.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.13,0:03:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm thinking of killing someone.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.10,0:03:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your former fiancée...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.54,0:03:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eva Heinemann.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.38,0:03:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry to have kept you waiting.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I rang her room, but she doesn't seem to be answering.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's her room number?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to send her a fax...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,so could you please tell me her room number?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.12,0:03:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's staying in room 402.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our fax number here is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.74,0:04:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,402...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Baul can't be reached at his\Noffice or on his cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.26,0:04:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how long you wait your\Npartner probably won't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.26,0:04:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,His excuse will probably go something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll probably say he became Tenma's attorney\Nin order to prove his innocence...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.60,0:04:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but he made a complete confession.\NOn top of that, he even escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He couldn't possibly defend a client like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.98,0:04:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll probably step down from being Tenma's attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to step down as well, Mr. Verdeman?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.02,0:05:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no intention of doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's true that Tenma did escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.86,0:05:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Before he escaped...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish he would've trusted me, his attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you trust Tenma, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.97,0:05:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you believe what happened in Munich?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you believe everything that Tenma has told me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you believe everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When I heard the news that Tenma escaped...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.89,0:05:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,it reminded me of that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The time he disappeared in Munich...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and tried to kill Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Something is about to happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.97,0:05:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why Tenma escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.61,0:05:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Please believe in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:06:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you believed in your father's\Ninnocence and became a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The phone's been ringing off the hook!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The media's in an uproar about whether\NVerdeman, the brilliant lawyer...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,will continue to defend Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Just tell everyone that I don't have any comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But that won't keep the media away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then just tell them that we'll hold a press conference...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,after we've re-examined all the facts and evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.04,0:06:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then, don't let anyone into the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but there's already a guest here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.82,0:06:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.18,0:06:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You let someone in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.82,0:06:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not seeing anyone today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.52,0:06:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, I told him that but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,he forced his way in and said he'd wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just who is it, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's someone from the BKA...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The BKA?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.64,0:07:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"Somewhere Over the Rainbow."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What a wonderful song.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly, it was the theme song\Nof the radio station your father managed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.85,0:07:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,406...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,405...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.06,0:07:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,404...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.84,0:07:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Room 402.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.28,0:07:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Guten Tag.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Guten Tag.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to the guest staying in this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.45,0:08:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to see the guest who was staying in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought they had checked out already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,While I was investigating Tenma's\Naffidavit protocols and such...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.41,0:08:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I thoroughly examined your reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.48,0:08:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Your very detailed reports, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:09:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard stories of the legal circle's\Ngolden boy, as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Verdeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.53,0:09:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You must've come here after receiving\Nnews of Tenma's escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.80,0:09:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.53,0:09:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any information to offer you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.54,0:09:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Escape, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.84,0:09:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually I've been on an extended vacation lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.64,0:09:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps this extended vacation...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.65,0:09:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,is also like an escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, I'm sorry, but I don't have time to socialize, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,However, perhaps it's a habit from\Nmy long years on the job...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but I just can't travel aimlessly around\Nthe world without any cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So I came up with a theme for the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The theme of this trip is this picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.14,0:09:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't have any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to ask you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:09:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, let's talk for a little longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:10:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told you that I don't have\Nanything to tell you about Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.69,0:10:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't come here regarding Tenma's case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I only heard the news about Tenma's\Nescape on my way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, because of this book.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I've become extremely curious about\Nthis picture book's author.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,However, this author had many pen names.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Of them, only the name Klaus Poppe was German.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So while I was investigating it out of curiosity...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the name of a certain individual\Nacquainted with Poppe came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A certain individual?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.19,0:10:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.56,0:10:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A program named "Fairy Tales of the World"\Naired on your father's radio station, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.74,0:10:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the records, in August of '66...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.14,0:10:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Poppe's "Where Am I?" aired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I've also looked through your father's trial records.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.31,0:11:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the greatest post-war case involving suspected\Nspies and shook all of West Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father had visited Czechoslovakia many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.49,0:11:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it was simply to meet with a picture book author...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.50,0:11:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the prosecution didn't mention any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.13,0:11:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I just thought that your father...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,may have been an old friend of this picture book author.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My father had many acquaintances through his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There were countless numbers of people\Nhe met with to discuss their shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you're saying they weren't all that close?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,However, when I investigated...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.02,0:11:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,klaus Poppe would usually hold other meetings\Nat his editorial company-owned house...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,or at an old farmhouse in the Czech countryside\Nthat Poppe used as a resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,However, meetings between him and your\Nfather were held at a particular mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:11:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A particular mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.70,0:12:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It was called the Red Rose Mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.44,0:12:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The mansion was never used under\Nthe name of klaus Poppe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.51,0:12:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever he used this mansion, he called himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a man who held an extremely powerful position.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,In the Czechoslovakian secret police, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.40,0:12:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.40,0:12:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Son of a spy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.41,0:12:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Son of a traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Son of a coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.76,0:12:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Go prove his innocence if you're pissed off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.09,0:12:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If the father's dirty, so is the son!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.10,0:13:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Son of a spy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All I want is to learn about the person\Nnamed Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anyone by that name!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father met with the picture book author,\NKlaus Poppe, at a particular mansion, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In Czechoslovakia, in '66?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A picture book author and a radio station manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all they were!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.36,0:13:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,While he called himself Klaus Poppe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the Red Rose Mansion was never used.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If he held a meeting with your father\Nat the Red Rose Mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.64,0:13:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that means he wasn't meeting him as Klaus Poppe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.81,0:13:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but as Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.48,0:13:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone from the Czechoslovakian secret police.\Nwith an extremely powerful position.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.99,0:13:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That means nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.15,0:14:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no interest in whether\Nyour father was a spy or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My father wasn't a spy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father must have known who\NFranz Bonaparta really was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Irrelevant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.17,0:14:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps your father was aware of what was\Ngoing on at the Red Rose Mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.38,0:14:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.78,0:14:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My father is innocent! He's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.72,0:14:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wish to talk, please contact me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said many times before...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.82,0:14:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no interest in whether\Nyour father was a spy or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.86,0:14:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to know about the person\Nnamed Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Father was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.41,0:14:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My father was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Verdeman, your wife is on the phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:14:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... your wife is calling from the maternity center...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.57,0:15:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're finally being discharged?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll come pick you up right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Start the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to what I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and start the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.64,0:15:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.68,0:16:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.39,0:16:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,First, let's calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me hear what you have to say, Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.52,0:16:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Eva?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.69,0:16:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Eva Heinemann?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.59,0:16:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.56,0:16:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Eva Heinemann?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.47,0:16:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you guys are trying to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"You guys"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.64,0:16:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stop the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.14,0:16:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Face forward and keep driving!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.24,0:16:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you guys want to kill Eva!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,kill Eva?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by "you guys"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.92,0:16:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You and that man Baul are working together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Baul?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.45,0:16:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the man I shot at the University of Munich library!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let there be any more victims!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you take Eva?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.17,0:16:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything started when I saved Johan's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Many lives have been taken since then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.57,0:17:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Countless numbers...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.85,0:17:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There have been too many victims!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stop the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you to keep driving!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is what you said true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.26,0:17:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true?! Can I believe you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My father...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.44,0:17:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,was suspected of being a spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.38,0:17:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, it was established that he was falsely charged, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.32,0:17:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,he really was a spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I believed in my father's innocence...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.06,0:17:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,chose to become a lawyer, and studied hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But I learned about it while I was still a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The absolute proof that my father was a spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since then, I couldn't trust anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.64,0:18:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's the "brilliant lawyer who gets all his clients off"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.58,0:18:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,"The legal circle's golden boy," my ass
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.05,0:18:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Crabbing a guy who doesn't believe in anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.02,0:18:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,really am the son of a spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.20,0:18:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When I found the notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When I found the notes he'd taken in the 60's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything that was written in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time I turned a page...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw everything I'd done out of belief\Nin my father shatter before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.22,0:18:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a doubt, my father was a spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.46,0:19:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Indecipherable codes enumerated there...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.06,0:19:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Numerous records of communication with\Nthe Czechoslovakian secret police...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.10,0:19:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The mysterious people my father\Nhad come into contact with...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Franz Bonaparta...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he also mention the Red Rose Mansion in there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.38,0:19:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I see now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.45,0:19:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That man named Baul probably approached\Nyou because he wanted those notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are they now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.29,0:19:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,At my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.57,0:19:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He was after your father's notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.18,0:19:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a letter addressed to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:20:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably predicted that you'd come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Help me, Kenzo."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.23,0:20:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"Please hurry and come to the Red Rose Mansion."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean that Eva's safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.70,0:20:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't her handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.37,0:20:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's playing around...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.24,0:20:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He's toying with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.92,0:20:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in the pile of old records.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"Somewhere Over the Rainbow."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take it with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,if it falls into the wrong hands, your father will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.33,0:20:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need it anymore.
