Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I believe in you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything you told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're trying to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.77,0:21:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do anything for you right now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.00,0:21:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,can I believe in you, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.58,0:21:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't trust people...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,who wave things like this around too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.60,0:21:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to believe...
